stairs or ladders. There are two ways to be
featured: in a single or in a grid/collage.
💥💥 Remember! 💥💥
We love the grids/collages as much as the
single features! And our followers like to see
both. 
ℹ️ You don't have to be a follower to be 
featured, but you should tag your photos 
with #stairsandsteps! 
Please invite other IGers, with photos of 
stairs and ladders, to tag their photos to 
our gallery. 😊 Have fun out there! 😊

"It's madness
To be always sitting around in sadness,
When you could be learning the steps of gladness.
You'll be happy when you can do
Just six or seven;
Begin to day!
You'll find it nice,
The quickest way to paradise.
When you practise,
Here's the thing to know,
Simply say as you go...
I'll build a stairway to Paradise
With a new step ev'ry day !
I'm gonna get there at any price;
Stand aside, I'm on my way !
I've got the blues
And up above it's so fair.
Shoes ! Go on and carry me there !
I'll build a stairway to Paradise
With a new step every day..."
Oh.....north wing...easterly facing!
